Storyline

Brothers, Killian and Crawford, find the hideout of deranged psychopaths terrorising 
the town in which they live. The psychopaths prey upon children and young adults as 
more and more go missing everyday. When finding a girl in the woods, Killian attempts 
to survive a night in the treehouse in which she has taken shelter. But can he get 
them both back to the town without being caught?
